const defaultInstitution = {
    name: 'SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust',
    tagline: 'Create A Good Future',
    established: '19 January 2022',
    phone: '+91 8310953760',
    whatsapp: '+91 8310953760',
    email: 'info@silmacademy.org',
    address: 'Moodushedde, Vamanjoor, Mangalore - 575028',
    logo: '/logo.png',
    favicon: '/logo.png',
    facebook: '#',
    instagram: '#',
    youtube: '#',
    twitter: '#',
    founderName: 'Advocate Shafeeq Saqafi',
    founderTitle: 'Founder',
    founderMessage: `Assalamu Alaikum Warahmathullahi Wabarakathuhu,

Welcome to SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust. Our institution was established with a noble vision — to create knowledgeable, ethical, and socially responsible individuals who can contribute meaningfully to society.

Education is the most powerful tool we can use to change the world. At SILM Academy, we believe in providing quality Islamic and modern education that empowers our students to excel in both spiritual and worldly pursuits.

Our commitment extends beyond the classroom. Through our charitable activities and community welfare programs, we strive to uplift those in need and create a positive impact in society.

We invite you to join us in this journey of knowledge, faith, and service.

Jazakallahu Khairan.`,
    founderImage: '/founder.jpg',
    advisorName: 'Shaik Aboobakar Musliyar (AP Ustha)',
    advisorTitle: 'Advisor',
    advisorMessage: `Assalamu Alaikum Warahmathullahi Wabarakathuhu,

It is with great pleasure that I associate myself with SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust as its advisor. This institution stands as a beacon of knowledge, combining the timeless wisdom of Islamic education with the practical benefits of modern learning.

The founders have shown remarkable dedication in establishing an institution that not only imparts academic excellence but also nurtures moral values and character development among students.

I pray that Almighty Allah blesses this institution, its management, teachers, and students with success in both this world and the hereafter.

May Allah guide us all to the straight path.`,
    advisorImage: '/advisor.jpg',
    welcomeText: `SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust is a premier educational institution established on 19 January 2022, dedicated to providing quality Islamic and modern education. Our institution strives to nurture students who are not only academically excellent but also morally upright and socially responsible.

We offer a comprehensive curriculum that integrates Quranic studies, Arabic language, Islamic studies, and moral education with modern academic subjects. Our qualified teachers and supportive learning environment ensure that every student receives the guidance they need to succeed.

Beyond education, SILM Academy is deeply committed to community welfare and charitable activities, serving as a pillar of support for those in need within our community.`,
    vision: 'Create knowledgeable, ethical and socially responsible individuals.',
    mission: 'Provide quality Islamic and modern education while serving society through charitable activities.',
    aboutHistory: `SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust was established on 19 January 2022 by Advocate Shafeeq Saqafi with a vision to create an institution that bridges the gap between traditional Islamic education and modern learning. Founded in Kerala, India, the academy started with a small group of dedicated students and passionate teachers.

Over the years, SILM Academy has grown into a respected educational institution, serving the community through its comprehensive educational programs and charitable initiatives. The trust continues to expand its reach and impact, guided by the principles of knowledge, faith, and service.`,
    aboutObjectives: [
        'To provide quality Islamic education rooted in authentic sources',
        'To integrate modern education with Islamic values and ethics',
        'To develop students with strong moral character and leadership skills',
        'To serve the community through educational and charitable activities',
        'To promote interfaith understanding and communal harmony',
        'To support underprivileged students through scholarships and aid',
        'To preserve and propagate Islamic knowledge and culture',
        'To create responsible citizens who contribute to nation building'
    ],
    heroSubtitle: 'Empowering minds through Islamic education and community service',
    donationMessage: 'Your generous contributions help us continue our mission of providing quality education and serving the community. Every donation makes a difference in shaping a better future.',
    bankDetails: `Bank Name: Canara Bank
Account Name: SILM Academy Public Charitable Trust
Account Number: 120027236542
